ActsAsOpenSocial
================
fix helpers for opensocial
only for mixi_mobile now

Example
=======
class ApplicationController < ActionController::Base
    opensocial_filter :mixi_mobile
    opensocial_filter true (= :mixi_mobile)
    opensocial_filter false (revert normal)
end

